{"tid":436290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(難怪港男?)  23歲中國留學生成日本校花","createTime":"2017-10-15T04:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T12:20:55.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9104d3fb9fb6f6d67daff2d016674a45cd3a3db8","tid":436290,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171014&amp;guid=57328973&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171014%26guid%3D57328973%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=4j05Xm5bLBYU9Xs%2FN1sKwy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e67a7a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171014%26guid%3D57328973%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=f718b01b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171014&amp;guid=57328973&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n【震驚中日】23歲中國留學生奪日校花 網友看透真相....<br />\n即時兩岸 <br />\n2017-10-14 00:01:51 HKT<br />\n<br />\n日本的「選美」活動無處不在，不過不知道為甚麼，這樣一個美女不少的地方，選美比賽選出來的人卻經常讓人出人意表，今次冠軍不是日本少女，而是中國少女拿下「后冠」！<br />\n<br />\n通常讀工科的學生給人的刻板印象，幾乎多為男生為主，如果工科學校有幾個面貌姣好的女生，應該會變成女神般的存在。而東京工業大學的「Miss Colle」選拔，相比其他大學選美比賽是多麼的值得令人「期待」，只不過這屆東京工業大學「Miss Colle」選拔就有些許特別，冠軍是由一名中國留學生壓倒性勝出。<br />\n<br />\n日本《MENCLUB》指出，東京工業大學的「Miss Colle」選拔，本屆第一名由中國女留學生艾芊芊奪冠，而第二名則是小林生成，最後就是第三位候選人網野hikari，雖然她白淨有氣質，不過有不少男學生表示，她和甜美的艾芊芊相比，可能還有段距離。<br />\n<br />\n來自江西的留學生、23歲的艾芊芊，她身高160cm，她最擅長是舞蹈。對於她奪冠，日本網友是非常認同，紛紛稱讚中國妹子顏值高：「好棒，果然中國水平不一般」；「果然中國妹子好可愛」；「真&bull;才色兼備」；「其他幾位是來搞笑的嗎？」。而中國網友對賽果亦議論紛紛：「之前的選美不怪你們，畢竟沒見過好看的&hellip;&hellip;」；「在中國大學會因為長相而自卑的女生，在日本居然可以當校花！而且，日本網民居然沒有罵zhi那女，太不愛國了！」但亦有人調侃說：「認為學校只有3個女學生，其他都是男學生的請舉手」；「只怪對手太弱雞了」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"241c798b4f4b34343f4dd20971777c4e7e6c612e","tid":436290,"uid":18949,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"相呢？"},{"pid":"841467a02b6c429a3de84779dd0d5abd943d1cc7","tid":436290,"uid":10707,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"同嗰兩件比咁緊係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742237faf411d0b503d56ba8c4b2beb1b1a45e49","tid":436290,"uid":96704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同嗰兩件比咁緊係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其餘兩個男人樣"},{"pid":"f89ff559103f3b213aebd2fbfe22327d04b140c6","tid":436290,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"我都係睇返飛田新地個post算"},{"pid":"c941a846ff557c37f9ea6950d437ce421ded24df","tid":436290,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"我就唔信三條女有得屌班支那狗唔屌啦"},{"pid":"b0fc949106df36bb89b9c2b666b9d7039d6b48e2","tid":436290,"uid":66610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"間學校得3個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4750d53acb19c2057256b330851d4a8c71fd4f9a","tid":436290,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"條LINK死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d4b8539a97179dbb3e3873f14702c35e1e8677","tid":436290,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條LINK死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新link<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171014/57328973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171014%2F57328973&d=4j05Xm5bLBYU9Xs%2FN1sKwy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=95d8fb33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F