。<br />\n<br />\n讀N賤豬排都變女神 依家男的也好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來讀n展變毒撚係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要當呢d 扒女神咁溝不如一個人好過"},{"pid":"50fbb23ba502e2250fba9df6b398d036eeb02fbf","tid":436290,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n讀N賤豬排都變女神 依家男的也好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學長也不錯，這是一個開放的時代<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/135638_8e1d9b7c546278946c8221ae4f3cf7a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F135638_8e1d9b7c546278946c8221ae4f3cf7a1.jpg&h=a558d243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引自： <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/117963795399803326957/posts/6W3KM1iUvwd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F117963795399803326957%2Fposts%2F6W3KM1iUvwd&d=4j05Xm5bLBYU9Xs%2FN1sKwy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8212fc6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/117963795399803326957/posts/6W3KM1iUvwd</a>"},{"pid":"b95c096bdba810200305303f9c11d6393018260f","tid":436290,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:00:48.000Z","msg":"朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e9c58a9dc408a17d348d05b784b32f5c59b597","tid":436290,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5515030309a943dd364e5500a59d971df8e691c","tid":436290,"uid":70060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4eadfea57c1eb6d8bd8082f7f74f43d7f40cdbbd","tid":436290,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「<span style=\"color: red;\">在中國大學會因為長相而自卑的女生</span>